<section class="how-does-it-work">
	<h2>Where do I start?</h2>

	<!--Screen Width <= 414 Width > 1280-->
	<div class="row how-does-it-work-row">
		<article class="col-sm-3">
			<img src="/Content/images/sign-up-icon.png" alt="" />
			<h4>Sign up</h4>
<p>To start, simply accept the terms and conditions.</p>
		</article>

		<article class="col-sm-3">
			<img src="/Content/images/spread-the-word-icon.png" alt="" />
			<h4>Spread the word</h4>
<p>Invite friends and family via email or Facebook by clicking the links on your online dashboard.</p>
		</article>

		<article class="col-sm-3">
			<img src="/Content/images/track-your-progress-icon.png" alt="" />
			<h4>Track your progress</h4>
<p>Check your online dashboard to view referral activity and rewards.</p>
		</article>

		<article class="col-sm-3">
			<img src="/Content/images/earn-rewards-wallet-icon.png" alt="" />
			<h4>Earn rewards</h4>
<p>Your friends have 30 days to add eligible Xfinity services and remain a customer in good standing for 90 days. Then you'll both receive Visa Prepaid Cards in the mail.</p>
		</article>
